features: Package Contains: This file folder organizer kit contains 1 folder of 36 pockets and 3 sheets of label stickers. The folder is 9.6” x 13.5”, which is suitable for US letter size documents. The thickness could be range from 1.96” to 20”.

Premium Material: Made up of high-quality polypropylene (PP) material. This accordion file organizer is thick, sturdy, durable and waterproof. There are cloth edge wraps to avoid sharp angles from hurting you.

Large Capacity: This folder provides 36 individual pockets for reliable partitioning and keeps all files tidy and organized. They could hold more than 4000 sheets of paper. One shop and no longer worry about file storage anymore.

Easy to Use: This file folder has no cover and could stay upright, just put your documents into the pocket and use the given stickers to mark each pocket. There is a desk pocket in front, which allows for storing pens, stickers and any other relevant stationery.

Wide Application: This file holder could store various kinds of documents, vouchers, paper, cards, receipts, painting work and so forth. It is a perfect document organizer for home, office and school.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Must Have Organizer - EOOUT 24 Pockets Accordian File Organizer
reviews.reviewText: As an antique booth owner, I can't stress enough how essential organization is to the smooth operation of my business. Recently, I discovered the EOOUT 24 Pockets Accordian File Organizer, and it has quickly become an invaluable tool for me.The EOOUT Accordian File Organizer boasts an impressive 24 pockets, making it a perfect solution for organizing a vast array of items. Each pocket is spacious and can comfortably accommodate various-sized documents, price tags, labels, or any other items you need to keep organized. This generous capacity allows me to store price tags and labels for all the different products I carry in my antique booth efficiently.One standout feature of this organizer is the included labels for each tab. These labels are a game-changer when it comes to quickly and accurately locating the items I need. I can easily label each pocket according to the product category, item type, or any other classification that suits my needs.I also appreciate the portable and durable design of this organizer. It's easy to carry to and from my antique booth, and the sturdy construction ensures that my important documents and labels remain well-protected. Whether I'm at the booth or working on pricing at home, this organizer is a reliable companion.If you're looking for an organization solution that can significantly improve your workflow I recommend the EOOUT Accordian File Organizer.
